'''六溴合锇(IV)酸铵'''是一种[[配位化合物|配位化合物]]，化学式为(NH<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub>OsBr<sub>6</sub>，它是[[立方晶系|立方]][[晶体|晶体]]，晶胞参数a=8.94 Å。<ref>Parlog, Constanta; Ciomartan, D.; Sandulescu, D.; Negoiu, D. Crystal structure of ammonium hexahaloenoosmiate and its dinitrogen compounds. ''Revue Roumaine de Chimie'', 1974. 19 (8): 1303-1306. ISSN: 0035-3930.</ref>它可以[[四氧化锇|四氧化锇]]、[[氢溴酸|氢溴酸]]和[[溴化铵|溴化铵]]为原料来制备：<ref name=Dwyer />
: OsO<sub>4</sub> + 10 HBr → H<sub>2</sub>[OsBr<sub>6</sub>] + 2 Br<sub>2</sub> + 4 H<sub>2</sub>O 
: H<sub>2</sub>[OsBr<sub>6</sub>] + 2 NH<sub>4</sub>Br → (NH<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub>[OsBr<sub>6</sub>] + 2 HBr

六溴合锇(IV)酸铵可以在异腈''<sup>t</sup>''BuNC的存在下被钠汞齐在[[四氢呋喃|四氢呋喃]]还原为''trans''-OsBr<sub>2</sub>(CNBu''<sup>t</sup>'')<sub>4</sub>。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Polyhedron|volume=3|issue=3|language=en|date=1984-01|pages=385–387|doi=10.1016/S0277-5387(00)88128-0|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0277538700881280|title=Synthesis and x-ray crystal structure of OsBr2(CNBut)4·2CH2Cl2|accessdate=2020-12-23|author=Richard A. Jones, Bruce R. Whittlesey, Jerry L. Atwood, William E. Hunter|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612021921/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0277538700881280}}</ref>它在[[氢溴酸|氢溴酸]]酸化的乙醇中和Ph<sub>2</sub>RAs回流反应，可以得到Os(III)的配合物OsBr<sub>3</sub>(Ph<sub>2</sub>RAs)<sub>3</sub>（R为烷基）。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Chemical Sciences|volume=89|issue=2|language=en|issn=0253-4134|date=1980-04|pages=101–108|doi=10.1007/BF02892993|url=http://link.springer.com/10.1007/BF02892993|title=Complexes of osmium with tertiary arsines and carbonmonoxide|accessdate=2020-12-23|author=K G Srinivasamurthy, N M Nanje Gowda, E G Leelamani, G K N Reddy}}</ref>它和[M(NH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>4</sub>]Cl<sub>2</sub>反应，可以得到[M(NH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>4</sub>][OsBr<sub>6</sub>]（M=Pd, Pt）。<ref>Gromilov, S. A.; Korenev, S. V. Synthesis and X-​ray diffraction study of [M(NH3)​4]​[OsBr6]. ''Journal of Structural Chemistry (Translation of Zhurnal Strukturnoi Khimii)'', 2002. 43 (3): 527-529. ISSN: 0022-4766.</ref>

